(1, 'Family Law', '/storage/marketing_law/1797754787700448.png', '<p><strong>Ready to take charge of your family law situation?</strong> At YourBestLawyer.com, we empower you with the knowledge and resources to confidently handle your legal challenges—whether it’s divorce, child custody, spousal support, or property division.</p>\n\n<p>Forget running from one law firm to another. Now you can explore your legal options and choose top attorneys—all from home. With upfront information, attorneys bidding for your case, and the freedom to set your budget, you’re in control. No more surprises, just expert representation tailored to your needs.</p>\n\n<p>Why settle for less when you can have the best? From cost-effective solutions to elite representation, we’ve got options for everyone.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Start your journey today with YourBestLawyer.com</strong> and feel the power of being in control of your legal future. Knowledge is power—and we’re giving it to you!</p>\n', '$', 'Enable', '2024-04-30 05:22:48', '2024-04-30 05:22:48'),
(2, 'DUI', '/storage/marketing_law/1797754816888715.png', '<p><strong>Facing a DUI charge?</strong> YourBestLawyer.com is here to give you the power to fight back! Arizona’s DUI laws are no joke—especially when a first offense may lead to a felony—but we’ve got you covered with everything you need to know.</p>\n\n<p>From misdemeanor to felony DUI, our platform is packed with easy-to-understand videos and insights. You’ll also learn the ropes of both misdemeanor and felony court procedures, so you’re always in control.</p>\n\n<p>No more wasting time on endless consultations! YourBestLawyer.com connects you directly with attorneys who bid for your case—at prices that match your budget. You get to choose the right attorney and take control of your legal journey.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Start your journey today with YourBestLawyer.com</strong> and take full control of your legal future. The power is in your hands—and we\'re giving you the knowledge to use it!</p>\n', '$', 'Enable', '2024-04-30 05:23:16', '2024-04-30 05:23:16'),
(3, 'Personal Injury', '/storage/marketing_law/1797754834980988.png', '<p><strong>Injured in a motor vehicle accident or slip and fall?</strong> YourBestLawyer.com has you covered! Our platform is packed with essential info to help you navigate your case, whether it’s dealing with property damage, bodily injury, or court procedures.</p>\n\n<p>With YourBestLawyer.com, you’re in control. Attorneys bid for your case using our backwards bidding system, where you choose the percentage premium from your settlement. No more surprises—just the best representation at prices you decide.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Get started today</strong>, and take charge of your personal injury case with YourBestLawyer.com!</p>\n', '%', 'Enable', '2024-04-30 05:23:33', '2024-04-30 05:23:33'),
