(5, 'Bankruptcy Law', '/storage/marketing_law/1800489247832188.png', '<p><strong>Dealing with overwhelming debt?</strong> YourBestLawyer.com has your back! Our platform provides clear, essential insights on Chapter 7, Chapter 13, and even complex Chapter 11 bankruptcies. Whether you\'re looking to eliminate debt or restructure payments, we have trusted attorneys ready to bid on your case, so you can choose the right one for your needs—all from the comfort of your phone or home computer.</p>\n\n<p>No need to stress about understanding bankruptcy laws—our resources break down everything, from eligibility to dischargeable debts and property exemptions. Plus, with our backward bidding system, you can choose your attorney\'s fee structure, putting you in control of the cost.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Take charge of your financial future today with YourBestLawyer.com.</strong> No matter the complexity of your bankruptcy, you’ll get expert help on your terms, at your price!</p>\n', '$', 'Enable', '2024-05-30 21:45:52', '2024-05-30 21:45:52'),
