hree options depending on your finances:</p>\n\n<ol>\n  <li>Attorneys with 2+ years of DUI experience. These are the most affordable, starting at $2,500–$5,000, including an MVD hearing but excluding trial. You can negotiate fees based on your finances, and attorneys will respond with offers.</li>\n  <li>Attorneys with 6+ years of DUI experience. Recommended if you need more expertise and trial representation. Fees range from $5,000–$8,500, including MVD procedures but excluding trial. You can submit your desired down payment, and attorneys will respond accordingly.</li>\n  <li>Top-tier attorneys with 10+ years of experience, including board-certified specialists. These are ideal for high-profile cases where dismissal is critical. Fees range from $8,500–$13,000, including MVD services but excluding trial. Recommended for professionals like doctors, attorneys, or CEOs where a conviction could be disastrous.</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>We hope you’ve gained more knowledge and can make the best decision. Every attorney, from novices to experts, aims to achieve case dismissal or the best possible outcome with minimal exposure. Best of luck, and we hope you have a great experience using our platform!</p>\n\n<p><strong>Credit:</strong></p>\n<p>Author: Felix Martinez</p>\n<p>Attorney Reviewer: Gordon Thompson</p>\n', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
