u seek dismissal at any cost. For example, if you are a doctor, attorney, actor, or CEO, and a conviction could ruin you or your company, these attorneys meticulously review every detail of the evidence and fight every aspect of the case with expert witnesses. Their fees range from $15,000 to $20,000, not including trial risks.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p>We hope you’ve gained valuable information to help you make the best decision regarding available lawyer options. Each attorney, from novice to expert, aims to achieve case dismissal or obtain the best possible result with minimal exposure. Best of luck, and may you have a great experience using our platform!</p>\n\n    <p class=\"credit\">Credit for this script:<br>\n    Author: Felix Martinez<br>\n    Attorney who checked for correct information and ensured no legal advice was given: Gordon Thompson</p>', NULL, NULL),
